Flora of Virginia
*Dalea urceolata* (Poir.) Brum.

near Stokesville, Augusta Co.
Scattered colonies for .7 mi. along
S bank of North River ca. 3/4 mi. SW of
Camp May Flather. With *Gaultheria*, *Epigaea*,
*Kalmia*, & *Thengieria* under *Pinus strobus*, *Tsuga*
& *Acer rubrum*.
(Stokesville Quad.) el. 1650 ft.
